args: I didn't think too much about it when we\nagreed to transport the repair supplies\nto the castle, but looking at all this now...
Wowser, that's some heavy-lookin' stuff!\nLift from the knees, buddy!
Sheesh, faeries have it easy.\nGet to just float there and watch.
If all you do is complain, the sun will be\nset before we finish here.
I think my back just cried a little...\nHey, wait, I got a, er, whatchamacallit...\nAn idea! We should hit up Jiang Ziya!

Hey, perfect timing! We wanna move
all this stuff, but it's a handful and a half;
how's about ya help us out with one
of those fancy relics of yours?
Ooo, it would be my pleasure!\nNow, feast your eyes on thisâ€”
Give something a little boop with this\nhandy-dandy rod, and it'll invert its\nnature!
Basically, super heavy stuff will become\nsuper not-heavy stuff! Talk about\nconvenient, right?
We would be in your debt.\nPlease, Jiang Ziyaâ€”proceed.
Hee hee! Yes, yes, leave it all to me,\nyour resident Qilin genius!

O power universal of the Qilin,
be bound by my solemn decree.
Inversion Rod. Nature paradoxical.
Strong and swift may you invoke your gift!
Okay, try picking that stuff up!
...Oh, my! It's light as a feather!
Now we're talkin'! All right, let's get\nmovin'!
Hm? It seems a cat was hiding amongst\nthe goods.
I-I... I don't DO cats. Way back, I had a\nsuper awful experience with one...
Pfft, carryin' a buncha crap? Sounds like\na pain in the cheeks. I'll pass.

Oh, perfect! Look here, we've got a
meathead on hand! Yo, Ranzal, get
your rear in gear and start liftin'
my share'a that crap already!
What are you even saying?!\nRanzal's not gonna go along withâ€”
W-wait, Elisanne! Ranzal, what is UP\nwith you?!
Don't yell like that! You're scaring me!\nMy heart can't take it!
Wha...? What happened to your nerves\nof steel...?
Okay, I dunno what's up with Elisanne,\nbut it's time to bring her backâ€”even if\nwe have to do it by force!
R-Ranzal?! Why are you hiding under that\nempty box?!
Am I in some bizarro world?

Elisanne is suddenly saltier than a bucket
of seawater, Ranzal probably just ruined
his favorite pair of underwear, and...
Wait. Don't tell me...
Did I accidentally reverse THEIR natures\nwith the Inversion Rod?!
Oh, Cleo! I'm so glad you're okayâ€”

But this looks like a huge pain in the butt.
I can't be bothered to do any work. If you
need me...think twice and find someone
else, as I'll be getting some shut-eye.
Oh no, everyone's all screwy!\nWhat the heck am I gonna do?!
Uhhh, Jiang Ziya? Why don't you just,\nI don't know... STOP THE DANG RELIC?!
O power universal of the Qilin,\nbe bound by my solemn decree.\nInversio Roâ€”wait! No, forget this!

I'm good on the whole Qilin relic thing!
Don't wanna look at 'em, don't wanna
touch 'em! I mean come on, they're
a huge pain!
...Right. You got flipped by the relic too,\nthen.

I stopped being a Sealer and left my
village so I could help everyone with
Qilin relics. But I don't care about
that anymore!
Ugh. What a mess.\nBut it's all good!
I'm the real hero, at the end of the day.\nI'll sort this out in half a jiffy!
Er, how's that? If you invert something\nand then invert the inverted thing,\nthen it's un-inverted, right...?
Y-yeah, it worked! The mere thought of\nQilin relics sets my heart aflutter!

O power universal of the Qilin,
be bound by my solemn decree.
Inversion Rod. Nature paradoxical.
Be your exertions henceforth suppressed!
What...? For some reason I feel as if\nI've been shirking my responsibilities.\nBut surely I would never!
And I feel like I just finished a stint as a\nspineless loser...
That's enough rest for now, I think.\nTime to get right to work.
What a relief... Everyone's back to normal.
ï¼‚Back to normalï¼‚? So we WERE under\nthe influence of a Qilin relic...
Yep. I got all inverted too, and it was\ntotally bananas.
And we were saved because Notte showed\nsome seriously quick wit! She's a sharp\none... Almost as sharp as me!
Heh heh! I've been feelin' pretty sharp\nfor a while now. It's weird, but I'm\nnot complaining!
Hm? Could it be that Notte was changed\nby the Qilin relic too?
Oh, y'know, maybe so! I do feel like I\nremember gettin' bonked with that rod.
Hey, wait... If I got inverted, and my\nmind's all sharp now... Does that mean\nI'm normally DULL?!
Oh man, you really saved our bacon!\nThree cheers for you, ya flyin' box'a rocks!
